  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the robata grill to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Grill the digestive biscuits for 2-3 minutes on each side, or until golden brown.",
    "Mince the garlic and mix with chives, salt, black pepper, and turmeric.",
    "Brush the coconut oil on the grilled biscuits and top with the garlic mixture.",
    "Squeeze a bit of lemon juice over the biscuits and sprinkle with cilantro.",
    "Top each biscuit with a dollop of cashew yogurt, a drizzle of honey, and a sprinkle of rice vinegar.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Optional: garnish with fresh ginger and a sprinkle of chives for extra flavor and color.",
    "Refrigerate any leftovers for up to 24 hours and reheat as needed."
